Sponsored by AWS

Lyft and AWS are redefining driver support with autonomous AI agents built on Amazon Bedrock. Through the AWS Generative AI Innovation Center, Lyft evolved its AI Assist platform into an intelligent, conversational system that helps drivers resolve most issues in under three minutes.

AWS is using AI for routine requests with great results and giving human agents the time to focus on complex cases, Lyft is delivering faster, fairer, and more accurate support.

Watch how AWS and Lyft are using generative AI to transform driver experience and power the future of mobility. https://aws.amazon.com/ai/our-story/
